# AI Project Delay Prevention Agent

An autonomous AI-powered project management assistant that proactively detects delivery risks in GitLab projects.

## Features

- Detects overdue GitLab issues
- Identifies blocked and critical tasks
- Calculates project delay risk scores
- Generates executive risk assessments
- Automatically posts intervention comments on high-risk issues

## Tech Stack

- Flask
- GitLab API
- Gemini API (with fallback AI risk engine)
- GitHub
- Render

## Running Locally

```bash
pip install -r requirements.txt
python app.py
